overview: From its first edits through to TURTLE 3 the crew of Turtle Productions documents the spirit of the street and in doing so, creates a testimonial to Viennese skateboard culture: a film, thatâ€™s like diary entries told in 4:3 format, preserved on MiniDV. Up close and unadorned. It is the texture of friendship, the feeling of endless vitality, with a soundtrack by Euroteuro.
title: TURTLE 3
